n\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32180,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/do-not-curse-wind\/","url_meta":{"origin":9840,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Weather: Do not curse wind directed by Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: A man cursed the wind in front of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him. The Prophet said, \u201cDo not curse the wind, for it only acts as it was commanded. Verily, whoever curses anything that does not deserve it, the curse will backfire against him.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28821,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/08\/allah-no-need-punish-yourself\/","url_meta":{"origin":9840,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Vows: Allah does not need you to punish yourself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, saw an old man walking with the support of his two sons. The Prophet said, \u201cWhat is the matter with this man?\u201d They said, \u201cHe has vowed to walk to the Ka\u2019bah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cAllah does not need this\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9840","targetHints":{"allow